Thought	#451.	 deep musing &c. (intent). in the mind, under consideration. Adv. all things considered. Phr. the mind being on the stretch
Judgment	#480.	 determinate, conclusive. Adv. on the whole, all things considered. Phr. a Daniel come to judgment" [Merchant of Venice]
Predetermination	#611.	 maturely considered
Predetermination	#611.	 with premeditation, deliberately, all things considered, with eyes open, in cold blood
Imperfection	#651.	 only, considering, all things considered, enough. Phr. surgit amari aliquid [Lat.].
